<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #f3f4f8; line-height: 1.8;">
    <table role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 10px;">
                <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                  
                    <!-- Main Container -->
                    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);">
                        <!-- Header -->
                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #7c3aed 100%); padding: 40px 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Account Verification</h1>
                            <p style="color: #e0e7ff; margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;">Please verify your email to get started</p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Main Content -->
                        <div style="padding: 48px 40px;">
                            <p style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 500;">
                                Dear <span style="color: #4f46e5; font-weight: 600;"><%= name %></span>,
                            </p>
                            <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                                Thank you for creating your account with us. We're delighted to welcome you to our community!<br><br>
                                Please verify your email address using the verification code below.
                            </p>

                            <!-- OTP Container -->
                            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fafafa, #f3f4f6); padding: 32px; text-align: center; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; border: 2px dashed #818cf8;">
                                <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;">Your Verification Code</p>
                                <div style="font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #4f46e5; font-family: 'Inter', monospace;"><%= otp %></div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Enhanced Warning Box -->
                            <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff7ed 0%, #ffedd5 100%); border: 1px solid #fed7aa; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.05);">
                                <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
                                    <div style="background-color: #fb923c; border-radius: 50%; width: 24px; height: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;">
                                        <span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">!</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p style="color: #9a3412; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 600;">Important Security Notice</p>
                                        <p style="color: #b45309; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
                                            This verification code will expire in <strong style="color: #92400e; font-weight: 600; background-color: rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.1); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">10 minutes</strong>. For your security, please do not share this code with anyone.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Help Text -->
                            <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; padding: 16px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; line-height: 1.6;">
                                If you did not create an account with us, please disregard this email or <a href="#" style="color: #4f46e5; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">contact our support team</a>.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>